OL,5, Pope Francis has warned the world is   
OL,6, "collapsing" due to climate change and 
OL,7, may be "nearing breaking point".       
OL,9,FThe pope criticised global             
OL,10,Fdecision-making bodies for being       
OL,11,Fineffective, as well as calling out    
OL,12,Fclimate deniers.                       
OL,14,FHis strongly-worded intervention has   
OL,15,Fbeen published in a major new update to
OL,16,Fhis landmark 2015 paper on the         
OL,17,Fenvironment..                          
OL,19,FHe described some damage from climate  
OL,20,Fchange as "already irreversible".      
